<HEADLINE> 49ers Sign QB Steve Stenstrom </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	SAN FRANCISCO (AP) -- The San Francisco 49ers signed former  
Stanford quarterback Steve Stenstrom to a two-year contract worth 
$1.2 million. 
</P>
<P>
	Stenstrom, 27, started seven games for the Chicago Bears last  
season, connecting on 112 of 196 passes for 1,252 yards and four 
touchdowns 
</P>
